description: Experience luxury living in South Boston’s vibrant heart at the newly renovated penthouse on 472 E 4th Street. This exquisite condo boasts three spacious bedrooms and bathrooms across two levels of sophisticated living. Revel in breathtaking views of downtown Boston from one of the three private outdoor spaces, including an expansive roof deck perfect for entertaining. Inside, find high ceilings, hardwood floors throughout, and a ductless HVAC system ensuring year-round comfort. The chef’s kitchen dazzles with custom cabinetry, sleek Quartz countertops, and premium Fisher & Paykel appliances. Each bathroom is a sanctuary featuring refined finishes that evoke spa-like tranquility. Added conveniences include generous closet space and in-unit laundry. With the sellers offering 2 years of rented parking, seize the opportunity to call this condo home!
